---
title: Cheesy Beef Burger & Kumara Fries with Beetroot Relish & Fried Egg
description: See life on the bright side with these sunny-side-up burgers. Juicy beef patties are topped with melty Cheddar cheese, a fried egg and a sweet beetroot relish. If that isn’t enough to satisfy your cravings, there’s baked kumara fries fresh out of the oven with a burger sauce for dipping.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/672d2ca01cd01ca44ffc05c3-c53824e2.jpeg
